      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span at least two load levels or two fixation configurations to bracket the COU operating envelope.",
      "rationale": "Testing was conducted at a single load configuration per ASTM F1717. Only one test condition was explored, which is below the required gradation. This shortfall is noted; the overall assessment proceeds because the single condition is representative of the worst-case clinical loading scenario."
